    "description": "体验一次在无尽虚空中的漂流小行星上开加油站的科幻故事。为愈发复杂的外星飞船提供服务、升级并拓展加油站业务，并通过选择塑造星系的命运！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/bf470429685c83db958696d16fa5539c.avif?t=1758039691\" width=580 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/e36b98be3c0405fd2224fbc4002ea61d.poster.avif?t=1758039691\" width=564 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/e36b98be3c0405fd2224fbc4002ea61d.webm?t=1758039691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/e36b98be3c0405fd2224fbc4002ea61d.mp4?t=1758039691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一开始只需要为外星飞船加加油，随后逐步扩大服务范围，引入更复杂的设施满足这些飞船的需求。尽可能高效快速地完成这些任务，在一天结束前尽量多赚些钱。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/415544caeecdf5cdf44f97ed3ef02b93.avif?t=1758039691\" width=580 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/342c6823ab7dd5aae99052fac97a563b.poster.avif?t=1758039691\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/342c6823ab7dd5aae99052fac97a563b.webm?t=1758039691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你的战略决策与各种互动将在更高层面影响故事发展，带来独特挑战与机遇。在日常运营加油站并与多种角色互动的过程中，会揭开各种秘密，纵横于错综复杂的星际政治网络。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/7a9cbc8e140f5eefe103e3e174e743f4.avif?t=1758039691\" width=580 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/55b874c99b8a67084e518dd8c28e039f.poster.avif?t=1758039691\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104980/extras/55b874c99b8a67084e518dd8c28e039f.webm?t=1758039691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>每天结束时，你必须向星系加油联盟缴纳会费。星系加油联盟是由加油站老板们组建的工会，致力于保护这群老板免受星系中邪恶势力的侵害。不过，他们可不会保护不交会费的家伙",
